<L>Ha adh-bheann nan uille-bhuadh,</L>
<L>Mathair <HI>Phembroke,</HI> Piuthar <HI>Philip:</HI></L>
<L>Ans gach Daan bith' orra luadh.</L>
<L>A Bhais man gearr thu &s;ios a coi-meas,</L>
<L>Beann a dreach, &s;a h' Juil, &s;a Fiach,</L>
<L>Bri&s;tidh do Bhogh, gun Fhave do &s;haighid:</L>
