</DIV3>
<DIV3 TYPE="epitaph">
<PB N="262" REF="281">
<HEAD>A Sailor's Epitaph in the Church-yard of Great <HI>Yarmouth, Norfolk.</HI></HEAD>
<LG>
<L>THO' <HI>Boreas'</HI> blow and <HI>Neptune</HI>'s waves</L>
<L>Have to&s;t me to and fro,</L>
<L>By GOD'S decree, you plainly &s;ee,</L>
<L>I'm harbour'd here below:</L>
<L>Where I mu&s;t at anchor lye</L>
<L>With many of our fleet;</L>
<L>But once again we mu&s;t &s;et &s;ail,</L>
